Pepper...and Salt
("California considers paying farmers not to grow in order
to conserve water." -- WSJ item)
                                                                                                       

   California's novel plan
   For water conservation
   Provided my young son
   With ecologic inspiration:
   "If farmers can get paid
   To not grow veggies, fruits and flowers,
   Then what will you give me, Dad,
   For not taking any showers?"
   -- Marshall E.Cobb.
